this is basically why i was screaming over the beard look
HES PRETTY AND HE KNOWS IT and it makes me so so glad
summary: Honestly everyone who misses the beard is valid cause it was a h o t look but what really made me ecstatic about Phil posting...
body: Honestly everyone who misses the beard is valid cause it was a h o t look but what really made me ecstatic about Phil posting that picture was that he’s the sort of person to worry over his appearance enough that changing his hair style took years of contemplation and anxiety to come over and it must be a casual thing to occur, going without shaving when he’s not filming for a bit but actually showing us that ‘changed look’, whether it’s a slow transition to reel us into or just a whim he’s been repressing and finally acted upon, it took a lot of confidence and bravery on his end and i was just very very glad that he had felt good enough about himself to post it.
